@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="bg-[#111418] text-white min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-8">
        <div class="bg-[#1a1e24] p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Privacy Policy for QuickShared</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6"><strong>Last updated:</strong> September 17, 2025</p>

            <p class="mb-6">Your privacy is important to us. It is QuickShared's policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you across our website.</p>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        <strong>File Data:</strong> We collect the files you upload, as well as associated metadata like filename, type, and size. We do not access the content of your files except where necessary to provide the service (e.g., to process uploads and downloads) or to comply with legal obligations.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">
                        <strong>Usage Information:</strong> We log information about how you use the service, such as your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and access times. This information helps us improve the security and functionality of our service.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">We use the information we collect to:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 mt-2">
                        <li>Operate and maintain the QuickShared service.</li>
                        <li>Allow you to upload, store, and download your files.</li>
                        <li>Monitor service usage to prevent fraudulent or abusive activities.</li>
                        <li>Improve the user experience and the overall quality of our services.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Information Sharing</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">We do not share your personally identifying information publicly or with third-parties, except in limited circumstances:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 mt-2">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Service Providers:</strong> Your files are stored using third-party services (e.g., cloud storage). These providers are required to protect your information and are not permitted to use your data for other purposes.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Legal Obligations:</strong> We may disclose your information if required to do so by law, subpoena, or other legal order.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Data Security</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        We use reasonable security measures to protect your information against loss, theft, unauthorized access, disclosure, copying, use, or modification. However, please remember that no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Your Rights</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        You have the right to request the deletion of your files. If you wish for a file to be permanently removed from our servers, please contact us.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        We may update our privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">7. Contact Us</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at: <code class="bg-gray-800 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded">[your-contact-email@example.com]</code>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>